metadata.name: Bankai
metadata.description: 420 High Indians blazin' on the Ethereum Blockchain! Chasing financial freedom and uplifting each other in the process! What started as a small collection that sold out through TikTok alone is now aiming to becoming the largest E-Commerce websites for smoke shop related paraphernalia. All high Indian holders get access to claim free items, heavily discounted products, legible for digital and physical giveaways, and much much more. Lets get lifted!
